# Design / layout mockups (kept on disk for local browsing during
# iteration; not committed and not shipped in the npm package).
# Convention: any file under public/ starting with `_dev-` is dev-only
# scaffolding. Accessible at http://localhost:PORT/_dev-<name>.html
# while the dev server runs; reuse the prefix for future mockups.
public/_dev-*.html
